===ετυμολογία===
From Greek '''[[έτυμον]] (etymon)''' (true sense), neuter of '''[[έτυμος]] (etymos)''' (real, true, actual) + Greek '''[[λόγος]] (logos)''' (word, speech, discourse) > Proto-Indo-European base '''[[*leg-]]''' (to collect).

